    "answerText2": "Based on your inputs, it will take you more than 40 years to save for the <span class='lf-bold'>$%emergencyFundGoal%</span> you will need for an emergency fund. Please adjust your inputs.",
    "answerText3": "The <span class='lf-bold'>$%amountSaveMonthly%</span> you can save monthly exceeds your available monthly cash (monthly income &minus; essential monthly expenses) of <span class='lf-bold'>$%availabelMonthlyCash%</span>. Please adjust your inputs.",
    "answerText4": "You should set aside <span class='lf-bold'>$%emergencyFundGoal%</span> for emergencies. By saving <span class='lf-bold'>$%amountSaveMonthly%</span> of your <span class='lf-bold'>$%availabelMonthlyCash%</span> available monthly cash, you will reach your emergency fund goal in <span class='lf-bold'>%monthsToReachGoal% %monthlabel%</span>.",
